From: Tomas Orsava <torsava@redhat.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Jan 2017 11:37:03 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Fixup various paths throughout the build and in distutils
 from "lib" to "lib64"

---
 Lib/distutils/command/install.py |  4 ++--
 Lib/distutils/sysconfig.py       |  6 +++++-
 Lib/site.py                      |  4 ++++
 Lib/test/test_site.py            | 11 +++++++----
 Makefile.pre.in                  |  2 +-
 Modules/Setup.dist               |  4 ++--
 Modules/getpath.c                |  6 +++---
 setup.py                         | 10 +++++-----
 8 files changed, 29 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

diff --git a/Lib/distutils/command/install.py b/Lib/distutils/command/install.py
index b9f1c6c..7b23714 100644
--- a/Lib/distutils/command/install.py
